  <title>SENIOR LECTURER/ LECTURER- INTERNAL MEDICINE</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/senior-lecturer-lecturer-internal-medicine</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;SENIOR LECTURER/ LECTURER- INTERNAL MEDICINE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;span lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/2085" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;maribek&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
